                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="p-5 flex-1 flex flex-col justify-between">
                    <div>
                        <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-1">
                            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white leading-tight">Dr. Marcus Johnson</h3>
